---
title: Rustic Italian Soup with Bacon & Cheesy Croutons
description: Mamma mia, we’re excited to bring you this rustic soup. It’s got all the good stuff: crispy Parmesan croutons, rich tomato and warming chilli. Partially blending your soup gives it a more ‘creamy’ consistency without adding anything extra - it’s one of our favourite little kitchen hacks!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b721c6eae08b5533c348885-dc3ee9c0.jpg
